result.name: Hong Kong Gold Coast Piazza

reviews.text: I love come to Gold Coast Piazza once a while to enjoy delicious dim sum at the restaurant. Convenient to come by public transport from Tuen Mun. This is a nice place to walk around and enjoy a relaxing weekend with friends and family. Parking space available but filled up really quickly during the weekend. Would recommend to make reservation if you are dining in one of the restaurants here.

The main character of the Gold Coast is the Paza where shops and restaurants are including McDonald. It’s a wonderful place to unwind or cool down after sun at the Golden beach nearby. Not only the place is adorned with beautiful garden but also lovely architectural buildings. This is again a nice and wonderful place to visit and photo taking during weekdays. The weekend is out of question packed with visitors and sometimes stalls selling food and handicrafts.
This is the plaza next to Gold Coast Hotel. This is the best place to go if you're in this part of Hong Kong
Excellent grocery store and lots of places to eat.  Decent view of the yachts towards the back, makes for great views during sunsets.

Mediocre food in a great waterside setting.  Sit on waterfront side possible.
Nice grocery store here.
